token_lists.title: Spacecraft
token_lists.description: "Fae spacecraft design, unsurprisingly, was influenced by the shapes and aerodynamics of flying insects. After all, these were creatures who could fly faster than the eye could see and navigate the most treacherous of routes. And with that in mind, they had created sleek, elegant ships that boasted pinpoint maneuverability and incredible speed. These were not just spaceships — they were flying masterpieces of engineering." Read more - https://medium.com/@wicgan/lightstreams-and-shortcuts-919fdf805840
